 Biographies
 ~~~~~~~~~~~
   Users can read and create biographies on ^nodetitle as a way of getting
to know users.

   To read someone's biography, use the <M>eet User or <.M><username>
commands.  Just type in the user's name and the system will display the
biography if it exists.

   If you want to enter a biography, or edit one already entered, type
<.E>nter <C>onfiguration <B>iography (.ECB).

